description:
Andou-san, as she is mostly referred to, has reached her 30th birthday anniversary as well without having had the chance to lose her virginity. This has made her become unsure, insecure, and shy about dating. She pretty much believes herself to be troubled. On top of that she learned how to do summon an AK-Field to prevent men from approaching her.
After all this, the gods decided to send her help in form of the sisters http://anidb.net/ch25323 [Pii-chan] and http://anidb.net/ch25324 [Kuu-chan].
name: Andou Natsu
